      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALLGOOD VINNIE (3) drew wider and worked to find the front before boxing on to finish second last start at Swan Hill. Came from the back line in winning two of his previous three outings so has been racing well. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run and see him tough to beat. ARE WEASLEY (5) continues to race well, placing in four of five starts since coming from the back line for a Bendigo win. Owns a good record at this venue. Major player. WOODLEA DIEGO NZ (4) has overcome some tough draws for a couple of good efforts at Melton of late, placing last time and winning from the second line three back. Should run a big race. AVEIRO (2) is a three-time fresh winner readied with a nice trial. Draws well so keep safe.",
